author: andreasmyth
msg: Dynamic loading of transport and binding factories and registration of wsdl extensions
in the sense of discovering information based on resources on classpath at time of bus initialisation ("phase 1").
Factories are only loaded when needed.

Solves the immediate problem having to either specify the list of all possibly needed  factories in configuration defaults and end up with instantiating more than will actually be needed, or restrict the list of pre-instantiated factories by always using configuration.
Handle URISyntaxException when attempting to set WSDL_DESCRIPTION property in message context.
